<paragraph pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
Taken in baited traps (
<bibRefCitation author="Jones, EG" journalOrPublisher="Marine Ecology Progress Series" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" pagination="75 - 86" publicationUrl="10.3354/meps251075" refId="B108" refString="Jones, EG, Tselepides, A, Bagley, PM, Collins, MA, Priede, IG, 2003. Bathymetric distribution of some benthic and benthopelagic species attracted to baited cameras and traps in the deep eastern Mediterranean. Marine Ecology Progress Series 251: 75 - 86, DOI: 10.3354/meps251075" title="Bathymetric distribution of some benthic and benthopelagic species attracted to baited cameras and traps in the deep eastern Mediterranean." url="10.3354/meps251075" volume="251" year="2003">Jones et al. 2003</bibRefCitation>
